item.title: automatic_refillstation
item.description: Automatic refill station (Internet connected) Register your interest Automatically dispenses fluid into refillable bottles. Choose your volume and walk away User friendly, and ideal for stores fulfilling internet orders Low energy consumption and small footprint Can be flexibly positioned above a bulk fluid container. Avoids manual handling of bulk fluid containers above ground height. Low level notifications and analytics

item.title: automatic_refillstation
item.description: Basic refill station (Open source) Register your interest Dispense cleaning fluids into refillable bottles. Fast, efficient electric pumping Low energy consumption and small footprint. Can be flexibly positioned above a bulk fluid container. Avoids manual handling of bulk fluid containers above ground height. Simple user interface There's only one button, no bells no whistles. Hold to dispense fluid, release to stop pumping.
